{"tid":1107317,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"盧偉聰：港獨影響社會安寧 會果斷執法","createTime":"2019-04-15T07:05:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-15T12:18:16.000Z","uid":28366,"like":1,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7a803406c6822186e261521ebcc16a6bc0346fdf","tid":1107317,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T07:05:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1452931_1_L_20190415134456.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1452931_1_L_20190415134456.jpg&h=7a871ce3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">盧偉聰稱，警方絕對不會姑息港獨行為。</span><br />\n<br />\n警務處處長盧偉聰表示，警隊對以後涉及港獨的違法行為會果斷執法，依法取締任何港獨組織。<br />\n<br />\n他在全民國家安全教育日香港研討會致辭時說，《基本法》列明香港為中國不可分離的一部分，任何鼓吹港獨的行為是違反《基本法》，港獨組織在多個場合進行宣揚港獨的活動，危害國家安全，任由港獨發布，會導致香港內部不穩，對社會安寧造成重大影響，警方絕對不會姑息港獨行為，因而依據《社團條例》禁止民族黨運作。<br />\n<br />\n盧偉聰又說，香港的繁榮穩定發展，全賴準確貫徹落實《基本法》及「一國兩制」的規定，香港人可享有高度言論自由，但自由不能沒有底線。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1452931-20190415.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1452931-20190415.htm&d=hmtFoPnP%2FIv5fOqUL3ZUaiMX%2BuEjOoKUanh%2Bi4Xf2cM%3D&h=c0818af1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1452931-20190415.htm&h=89785426\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1452931-20190415.htm</a>"},{"pid":"0cae550d1c0edb58759c233878cc598def134212","tid":1107317,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T07:05:45.000Z","msg":"100% - 0.01% = ?"},{"pid":"933986362e4631f68eac419918fe2096ba890078","tid":1107317,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T07:24:35.000Z","msg":"違犯基本法有咩罰則?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a3ab58888dfae3610466b4fcb61e7e93831da02","tid":1107317,"uid":3241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"sc